          "text": "That's because your service is set to read config from `apprunner.yaml`. The docs confirm: **\"if you decide to use a configuration file, additional settings are hidden in the console — App Runner reads them from the file.\"**\n\nThe env vars must go in `apprunner.yaml` itself. For sensitive values you have two options:\n\n**Option A (quick, for testing only — don't commit to public git):** Add them as plaintext directly in the yaml:",
